import Button from "@mui/material/Button";
import Box from "@mui/material/Box";
import TextField from "@mui/material/TextField";
import Typography from "@mui/material/Typography";
import useClient from "../pages/client/service";
export default function SignUpForm(props) {
  return (
    <Box
      sx={{
        mx: 4,
        display: "flex",
        flexDirection: "column",
        alignItems: "center",
      }}
    >
      <Typography component="h1" variant="h5">
        Add Client
      </Typography>
      <Box noValidate sx={{ mt: 1 }}>
        <TextField
          margin="normal"
          required
          fullWidth
          id="identityNumber"
          label="Identity Number"
          name="identityNumber"
          autoFocus
          onChange={props.onChange}
        />
        <Box
          sx={{
            display: "flex",
            gap: "0.5rem", // Espace entre les champs
          }}
        >
          <TextField
            margin="normal"
            required
            id="firstName"
            label="First Name"
            name="firstName"
            fullWidth
            onChange={props.onChange}
          />
          <TextField
            margin="normal"
            required
            id="lastName"
            label="Last Name"
            name="lastName"
            fullWidth
            onChange={props.onChange}
          />
        </Box>
        <Box
          sx={{
            display: "flex",
            gap: "0.5rem", // Espace entre les champs
          }}
        >
          <TextField
            margin="normal"
            required
            id="phoneNumber"
            label="Phone Number"
            name="phoneNumber"
            type="string"
            fullWidth
            onChange={props.onChange}
          />
          <TextField
            margin="normal"
            required
            id="email"
            label="Email"
            name="email"
            type="email"
            fullWidth
            onChange={props.onChange}
          />
        </Box>
        <Typography component="h2" variant="h6" sx={{ mt: 3 }}>
          Address Details
        </Typography>
        <Box
          sx={{
            display: "flex",
            gap: "0.5rem", // Espace entre les champs
          }}
        >
          <TextField
            margin="normal"
            required
            fullWidth
            id="country"
            label="Country"
            name="address.country"
            onChange={props.onChange}
          />
          <TextField
            margin="normal"
            required
            fullWidth
            id="city"
            label="City"
            name="address.city"
            onChange={props.onChange}
          />
          <TextField
            margin="normal"
            required
            fullWidth
            id="street"
            label="Street"
            name="address.street"
            onChange={props.onChange}
          />
          <TextField
            margin="normal"
            required
            fullWidth
            id="buildingNumber"
            label="Building Number"
            name="address.buildingNumber"
            type="number"
            onChange={props.onChange}
          />
        </Box>
        <Button
          type="submit"
          onClick={props.add}
          variant="contained"
          sx={{ mt: 3, mb: 1 }}
        >
          Add Client 
        </Button>
      </Box>
    </Box>
  );
}
